Modification of SA in OpenFOAM 5 to fallback to implementation in OpenFOAM 2.4 and below

OF5 SA with no ft2 (base implementation)
OF24 and below SA with fv3

More info at:
https://turbmodels.larc.nasa.gov/spalart.html 


To compile the new model:

**********************************
Modify the file
TurbulenceModels/compressible/turbulentFluidThermoModels/turbulentFluidThermoModels.C

and add in RAS models before the orignal SpalartAllmaras:
#include "my_SpalartAllmaras.H"
makeRASModel(my_SpalartAllmaras);
**********************************


**********************************
Modify the file
TurbulenceModels/incompressible/turbulentTransportModels/turbulentTransportModels.C

and add in RAS models before the orignal SpalartAllmaras:
#include "my_SpalartAllmaras.H"
makeRASModel(my_SpalartAllmaras);
**********************************


**********************************
Copy the files create the directory
TurbulenceModels/turbulenceModels/RAS/my_SpalartAllmaras/

and copy the se files into the newly created directory
my_SpalartAllmaras.H
my_SpalartAllmaras.C
**********************************

**********************************
Create symbolic links to the previous files of copy the files in the directory (it is better to create symbolic links):
TurbulenceModels/turbulenceModels/lnInclude



